graph TD

    subgraph Clients
        WC1["Wayland Client (App)"]
        WC2["Wayland Client (App)"]
    end

    WComp["Wayland Compositor"]

    subgraph Kernel
        EVDEV["evdev (Input Events)"]
        KMS["KMS (Display Control)"]
    end

    Mesa["Mesa / Vulkan / GPU Drivers"]

    %% INPUT FLOW
    EVDEV -->|input events| WComp

    %% INPUT DELIVERY TO CLIENTS
    WComp -->|keyboard / pointer events| WC1
    WComp -->|keyboard / pointer events| WC2

    %% RENDERING FLOW
    WC1 -->|render via GPU APIs| Mesa
    WC2 -->|render via GPU APIs| Mesa
    Mesa -->|DMA-BUF buffers| WComp

    %% DISPLAY OUTPUT
    WComp -->|composite / scanout| KMS
    KMS --> Display["Monitor / Display Hardware"]

    %% OPTIONAL INDIRECT CLIENT COMMUNICATION
    WC1 -. clipboard / drag-drop .-> WComp
    WC2 -. clipboard / drag-drop .-> WComp